the movies were entertaining. i enjoyed watching them. my favorite is the Secret Life of Bees but they were all good in their own ways

O yes it's ladies night. Woman Thou Art Loose, Jason's Lyric, Out Of Time, and Secret Life Of Bees, all on one disc. That's saturday night with popcorn and juice and all the ladies in the house. I just have to sit in the  corner and be quiet. But, they're very pleasant movies, so I don't mind.
In Atlanta hair extension salon pretty much every client loves these movies about strong women. Nothing better than a glass of wine, some perfect hair, and a great chick-flick.
This collection is a great value; 4 movies in one set with some of the best African American actresses of today.  Get your tissues, snacks, & your girlfriends together for a fantastic movie night!
